	(37112, 0, 0, 'Torin Kir talsa Krast\'ven!', 14, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'OCC Text for Wayward Fire Elemental', 0),
	(37112, 1, 0, 'TORIN KIR TALSA KRAST\'VEN', 12, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'Aggro Text for Wayward Fire Elemental', 0),
	(37113, 0, 0, '<static> Is this thing on? Hello?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Text during flying', 0),
	(37113, 1, 0, 'Ahh, there you are. Hello! I figured that, while you\'re flying to Kharanos, I\'d give you some data about what\'s going on outside of Coldridge Valley.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'text during flying', 0),
	(37113, 2, 0, 'And if you\'ll look to your left, you\'ll see that the gnomes have retaken Gnomeregan. Hooray for us!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'text during flying', 0),
	(37113, 3, 0, 'If you thought you had problems with trolls in Coldridge, wait \'til you get to Kharanos! That big cataclysm got the trolls all stirred up out here.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'text during flying', 0),
	(37113, 4, 0, 'It seems you Coldridge folks are dreadfully under-informed about the events of the last few days.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'text during flying', 0),
	(37113, 5, 0, 'There\'s plenty else going on out here, too. We\'ve opened up the path to the airport, there\'s rumors of Dark Irons in the east... oh, and I think something weird is going on with that dwarf king, Magni. Might want to check it out.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'text during flying', 0),
	(37113, 6, 0, 'And here we are! Welcome to Kharanos! Watch your step on the way out.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'text during flying', 0),
	(37119, 0, 0, 'This is our final stand. What happens here will echo through the ages. Regardless of outcome, they will know that we fought with honor. That we fought for the freedom and safety of our people!', 14, 0, 0, 22, 0, 16653, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring - SAY_TIRION_INTRO_1', 0),
	(37119, 1, 0, 'Remember, heroes, fear is your greatest enemy in these befouled halls. Steel your heart and your soul will shine brighter than a thousand suns. The enemy will falter at the sight of you. They will fall as the light of righteousness envelops them!', 14, 0, 0, 22, 0, 16654, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring - SAY_TIRION_INTRO_2', 37028),
	(37119, 2, 0, 'Our march upon Icecrown Citadel begins now!', 14, 0, 0, 22, 0, 16655, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring - SAY_TIRION_INTRO_3', 37029),
	(37119, 3, 0, 'ARTHAS! I swore that I would see you dead and the Scourge dismantled! I\'m going to finish what I started at Light\'s Hope!', 14, 0, 0, 22, 0, 16656, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring - SAY_TIRION_INTRO_4', 37031),
	(37119, 4, 0, 'The power of the Light knows no bounds, Saurfang. His soul is under great strain, but he lives - for now.', 12, 0, 0, 1, 0, 16658, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring - SAY_TIRION_INTRO_5', 37056),
	(37119, 5, 0, 'By the Light, it must be so!', 12, 0, 0, 5, 0, 16657, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring - SAY_TIRION_INTRO_A_5', 37038),
	(37122, 0, 0, 'Never... could reach... the top shelf...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16586, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_DEATH', 37074),
	(37122, 1, 0, 'You miserable fools never did manage to select a decent bat wing.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16587, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_RESURRECTED', 37076),
	(37122, 2, 0, 'THAT was for bringing me spoiled spider ichor!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16588, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_KILL', 0),
	(37122, 3, 0, 'Don\'t... let Finklestein use me... for his potions...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16589, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_SECOND_DEATH', 37077),
	(37122, 4, 0, 'The loss of our comrades was unpreventable. They lived and died in the service of the Argent Crusade.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16590, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_SURVIVE_TALK', 37534),
	(37122, 5, 0, 'Even dying here beats spending another day collecting reagents for that madman, Finklestein.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16585, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_INTRO_2', 36948),
	(37123, 0, 0, 'No amount of healing can save me now. Fight on, brothers...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16810, 'Captain Brandon - SAY_BRANDON_DEATH', 37665),
	(37123, 1, 0, 'What? This strength...? All of the pain is gone! You... must join me in the eternal embrace of death!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16811, 'Captain Brandon - SAY_BRANDON_RESURRECTED', 0),
	(37123, 2, 0, 'It doesn\'t hurt anymore, does it?', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16812, 'Captain Brandon - SAY_BRANDON_KILL', 0),
	(37123, 3, 0, 'I\'m sorry...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16813, 'Captain Brandon - SAY_BRANDON_SECOND_DEATH', 37659),
	(37123, 4, 0, 'You have done much in this war against the Scourge. May the light embrace you.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16815, 'Captain Brandon - SAY_BRANDON_SURVIVE_TALK', 37533),
	(37124, 0, 0, 'Please... burn my remains. Let me live warm in the afterlife...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16844, 'Captain Grondel - SAY_GRONDEL_DEATH', 37666),
	(37124, 1, 0, 'No! Why was I denied a death by flame? You must all BURN!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16845, 'Captain Grondel - SAY_GRONDEL_RESURRECTED', 37667),
	(37124, 2, 0, 'Can you feel the burn?', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16846, 'Captain Grondel - SAY_GRONDEL_KILL', 37660),
	(37124, 3, 0, 'What... have I done? No!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16847, 'Captain Grondel - SAY_GRONDEL_SECOND_DEATH', 37661),
	(37124, 4, 0, 'What can possibly redeem this unholy place? Thank you...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16849, 'Captain Grondel - SAY_GRONDEL_SURVIVE_TALK', 0),
	(37125, 0, 0, 'It was... a worthy afterlife.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16998, 'Captain Rupert - SAY_RUPERT_DEATH', 37668),
	(37125, 1, 0, 'There is no escaping the Lich King\'s will. Prepare for an explosive encounter!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16999, 'Captain Rupert - SAY_RUPERT_RESURRECTED', 37669),
	(37125, 2, 0, 'So that\'s what happens when you stand too close to a bomb!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17000, 'Captain Rupert - SAY_RUPERT_KILL', 0),
	(37125, 3, 0, 'What an... explosive ending!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17001, 'Captain Rupert - SAY_RUPERT_SECOND_DEATH', 37663),
	(37125, 4, 0, 'Beware the dangers that lie ahead... and do try to remain in one piece.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17003, 'Captain Rupert - SAY_RUPERT_SURVIVE_TALK', 37536),
	(37126, 0, 0, 'You may have once fought beside me, Crok, but now you are nothing more than a traitor. Come, your second death approaches!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17017, 'Sister Svalna - SAY_EVENT_START', 0),
	(37126, 1, 0, 'Miserable creatures! Die!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17018, 'Sister Svalna - SAY_KILL_CAPTAIN', 0),
	(37126, 2, 0, 'Foolish Crok. You brought my reinforcements with you. Arise, Argent Champions, and serve the Lich King in death!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17019, 'Sister Svanlna - SAY_RESURRECT_CAPTAINS', 0),
	(37126, 3, 0, 'Come, Scourgebane. I\'ll show the master which of us is truly worthy of the title of "Champion"!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17020, 'Sister Svalna - SAY_AGGRO', 0),
	(37126, 4, 0, 'What a pitiful choice of an ally, Crok!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17021, 'Sister Svalna - SAY_KILL', 0),
	(37126, 5, 0, 'What? They died so easily? No matter.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17022, 'Sister Svalna - SAY_CAPTAIN_DEATH', 0),
	(37126, 6, 0, 'Perhaps... you were right, Crok.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17023, 'Sister Svalna - SAY_DEATH', 0),
	(37126, 7, 0, '%s has impaled $N!', 41, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Sister Svalna - EMOTE_SVALNA_IMPALE', 37977),
	(37129, 0, 0, 'Ready your arms, my Argent Brothers. The Vrykul will protect the Frost Queen with their lives.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16819, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_INTRO_1', 36945),
	(37129, 1, 0, 'Enough idle banter! Our champions have arrived - support them as we push our way through the hall!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16820, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_INTRO_3', 36946),
	(37129, 2, 0, 'Draw them back to us, and we\'ll assist you.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16821, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_COMBAT_WP_0', 37013),
