	(20129, 1, 0, 'We do not know if the Caverns of Time have always been accessible to mortals. Truly, it is impossible to tell as the Timeless One is in perpetual motion, changing our timeways as he sees fit. What you see now may very well not exist tomorrow. You may wake up and have no memory of this place.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'WHISPER_CUSTODIAN_2', 0),
	(20129, 2, 0, 'It is strange, I know... Most mortals cannot actually comprehend what they see here, as often, what they see is not anchored within their own perception of reality.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'WHISPER_CUSTODIAN_3', 0),
