	(36853, 12, 0, 'You are fools to have come to this place. The icy winds of Northrend will consume your souls!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17007, 'Sindragosa - SAY_AGGRO', 37511),
	(36853, 13, 0, 'Aaagh! It burns! What sorcery is this!?', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17015, 'Sindragosa - SAY_RESPITE_FOR_A_TORMENTED_SOUL', 38550),
	(36853, 14, 0, 'Now, feel my master\'s limitless power and despair!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17016, 'Sindragosa - SAY_PHASE_2', 37109),
	(36853, 15, 0, '%s fires a frozen orb towards $N!', 41, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Sindragosa - EMOTE_WARN_FROZEN_ORB', 38672),
	(36855, 17, 0, 'It is a weakness; a crippling flaw....  A joke played by the Creators upon their own creations.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17268, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_INTRO_4', 38135),
	(36855, 18, 0, 'What is this disturbance? You dare trespass upon this hallowed ground? This shall be your final resting place!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16868, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_AGGRO', 38122),
	(36913, 1, 0, 'He watches your every move...', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eye of the Lich King - Whisper', 38354),
	(36939, 14, 0, 'What is that? Something approaching in the distance.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17089, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_3', 37692),
	(36939, 15, 0, 'You answer to Saurfang now!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17091, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_5', 37697),
	(36939, 16, 0, 'You will know our business soon. Kor\'kron, ANNIHILATE THEM!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17092, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_6', 37698),
	(36939, 17, 0, 'This is not your battle, dwarf. Back down or we will be forced to destroy your ship.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17083, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_A', 37685),
	(36948, 15, 0, 'Not me battle? I dunnae who ye think ye are, mister, but I got a score to settle with Arthas and yer not gettin\' in me way! FIRE ALL GUNS! FIRE! FIRE!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16968, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_MURADIN_INTRO_7', 37683),
	(36948, 16, 0, 'Move yer jalopy or we\'ll blow it out of the sky, orc! The Horde\'s got no business here.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16969, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_MURADIN_INTRO_H', 37699),
	(36954, 10, 0, 'Your allies have arrived, Jaina, just as you promised. You will all become powerful agents of the Scourge..', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17212, 'Lich King SAY_LICH_KING_AGGRO_A', 37172),
	(36954, 11, 0, 'Arise minions.  Do not let them pass.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17216, 'Lich King SAY_LICH_KING_GHOUL', 38669),
	(36954, 12, 0, 'Minions, sieze them.  Bring their corpses back to me.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17222, 'Lich King SAY_LICH_KING_ABON', 38670),
	(36955, 10, 0, 'He is too powerful. We must leave this place at once! My magic can hold him in place for only a short time. Come quickly, heroes!', 14, 0, 100, 1, 0, 16644, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_AGGRO', 36821),
	(36955, 11, 0, 'Another ice wall! Keep the undead from interrupting my incantations so that I may bring this wall down.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16608, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_WALL_02', 38537),
	(36955, 12, 0, 'Your barriers can\'t hold us back much longer, monster! I will shatter them all!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16610, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_WALL_04', 38539),
	(36955, 13, 0, 'It... It\'s a dead end. We have no choice but to fight. Steel yourselves, heroes, for this is our last stand!', 14, 0, 100, 1, 0, 16647, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_TRAP', 36992),
	(36990, 5, 0, 'Frostmourne? The Lich King is never without his blade. If you are lying to me...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17034, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_OUTRO_4', 36846),
	(37119, 6, 0, 'This is our final stand. What happens here will echo through the ages. Regardless of outcome, they will know that we fought with honor. That we fought for the freedom and safety of our people.$B$BRemember, hero, fear is your greatest enemy in these befouled halls. Steel your heart and your soul will shine brighter than a thousand suns. The enemy will falter at the sight of you. They will fall as the light of righteousness envelops them!', 14, 0, 0, 22, 0, 16653, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring - SAY_TIRION_INTRO_1', 36923),
	(37124, 5, 0, 'What can possibly redeem this unholy place? Thank you.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16849, 'Captain Grondel - SAY_GRONDEL_SURVIVE_TALK', 37535),
	(37125, 5, 0, 'So that\'s what happens what you stand too close to a bomb!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17000, 'Captain Rupert - SAY_RUPERT_KILL', 37662),
	(37126, 9, 0, 'They died so easily. No matter.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17022, 'Sister Svalna - SAY_CAPTAIN_DEATH', 37163),
	(37126, 10, 0, '%s has impaled $N!', 41, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Sister Svalna - EMOTE_SVALNA_IMPALE', 37977),
	(37129, 9, 0, 'Augh! I must rest for a moment.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16826, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_WEAKENING_GAUNTLET', 37164),
	(37129, 10, 0, 'Champions! I cannot hold her back any longer.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16827, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_WEAKENING_SVALNA', 37165),
	(37187, 19, 0, 'We named him Dranosh - It means "Heart of Draenor" in orcish. I would not let the warlocks take him. My boy would be safe, hidden away by the elders of Garadar.', 12, 0, 0, 1, 0, 17098, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_5', 37640),
	(37187, 20, 0, '%s charges!', 16, 0, 0, 53, 0, 17104, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_8', 37643),
	(37200, 16, 0, 'Don\'t force me hand, orc. We can\'t let ye pass.', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16972, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_7', 37524),
	(37221, 12, 0, 'The chill of this place... I can feel my blood freezing.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16631, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_1', 37591),
	(37221, 13, 0, 'What is that! Up ahead! Could it be? Heroes, at my side!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16632, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_2', 37592),
	(37221, 14, 0, 'Frostmourne: the blade that destroyed our kingdom...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16633, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_3', 37593),
	(37221, 15, 0, 'Stand back! Touch that blade and your soul will be scarred for all eternity! I must attempt to commune with the spirits locked away within Frostmourne. Give me space. Back up, please.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16634, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_4', 37594),
	(37221, 16, 0, 'Uther! Dear Uther! I... I\'m so sorry.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16635, 'Jaina SAY_JAINA_INTRO_5', 37595),
	(37223, 9, 0, 'I... I don\'t believe it! Frostmourne stands before us - unguarded - just as the gnome claimed. Come, heroes!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17049, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_INTRO_1', 37568),
	(37223, 10, 0, 'Uther... Uther the Lightbringer. How...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17052, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_INTRO_4', 37571),
	(37223, 11, 0, 'The Lich King is here? Then my destiny shall be fulfilled on this day!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17053, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANAS_INTRO_5', 37572),
	(37225, 16, 0, 'Jaina, you haven\'t much time. The Lich King sees what the sword sees. He will be here shortly.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16667, 'Uther SAY_UTHER_INTRO_A2_2', 37604),
	(37226, 5, 0, 'Foolish girl. You seek that which I killed long ago. He is merely a ghost now. A faint echo in my mind...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17229, 'Lich King SAY_LK_JAINA_INTRO_END', 37617),
	(37226, 6, 0, 'I will not make the same mistake again, Sylvanas. This time there will be no escape. You will all serve me in death!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17228, 'Lich King SAY_LK_SYLVANAS_INTRO_END', 37616),
	(37495, 4, 0, 'So that\'s what happens what you stand too close to a bomb!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17000, 'Captain Rupert - SAY_RUPERT_KILL', 37662),
	(37554, 9, 0, 'He\'s... too powerful. Heroes, quickly... come to me! We must leave this place at once! I will do what I can to hold him in place while we flee.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17058, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANA_AGGRO', 37168),
	(37554, 10, 0, 'No wall can hold the Banshee Queen. Keep the undead at bay, heroes. I will tear this barrier down!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17029, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANA_WALL_01', 38540),
	(37554, 11, 0, 'Another barrier? Stand strong, champions. I will bring the wall down.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17030, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANA_WALL_02', 38541),
	(37554, 12, 0, 'You won\'t impede our escape, fiend! Keep the undead off me while I bring this barrier down.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17032, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANA_WALL_04', 38543),
	(37554, 13, 0, 'We\'re almost there... Don\'t give up!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17060, 'Sylvanas SAY_SYLVANA_ESCAPE_02', 38538),
	(37592, 3, 0, 'Brave champions, we owe you our lives, our freedom.... Though it be a tiny gesture in the face of this enormous debt, I pledge that from this day forth, all will know of your deeds, and the blazing path of light you cut through the shadow of this dark citadel.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Gorkun SAY_GORKUN_OUTRO_1', 37320),
	(37592, 4, 0, 'This day will stand as a testament not only to your valor, but to the fact that no foe, not even the Lich King himself, can stand when Alliance and Horde set aside their differences and-', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Gorkun SAY_GORKUN_OUTRO_2', 37321),
	(37596, 6, 0, 'The Argent Crusade and the Knights of the Ebon Blade have assaulted the gates of the Icecrown Citadel and are preparing for a massive attack upon the Scourge. Our mission is a bit more subtle, but equally as important.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17038, 'sylvanas SAY_INTRO_1', 37380),
	(37596, 7, 0, 'With the attention of the Lich King turned towards the front gate, we\'ll be working our way through the side in search of information that will enable us to defeat him - once and for all.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17039, 'sylvanas SAY_INTRO_2', 37381),
	(37596, 8, 0, 'We will cut a swath of destruction through this cursed place and find a way to enter the Halls of Reflection. If there is anything of value to be found here, it will be found in the halls.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 17041, 'sylvanas SAY_INTRO_4', 37383),
